Config-Lite version 0.03
========================

Simple config load module.
Code is clean and no dependence, so the module is easy to use and install.
flock() inside.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module no other modules and libraries.

